                            <comment id="11756" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Fri, 10 Dec 2004 05:37:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well-spotted; it should receive a parentMessageSource reference. However, this doesn&apos;t come into effect if the parent is an AbstractApplicationContext too: getBean(&quot;messageSource&quot;) will find the parent&apos;s MessageSource bean in this case, if none defined in the child context. So the context will never set up a fallback StaticMessageSource in such a case.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
